concept_explanation.grpc_service:
**Implementing a gRPC server with @GrpcService:**

```java
// Proto-generated: RiskServiceGrpc.RiskServiceImplBase
// Extend it, annotate with @GrpcService:

@GrpcService
public class RiskServiceImpl extends RiskServiceGrpc.RiskServiceImplBase {

    @Autowired
    private RiskCalculator riskCalculator;

    @Override
    public void checkPayment(CheckRequest req, StreamObserver<CheckResponse> responseObserver) {
        try {
            // 1. Business logic:
            RiskScore score = riskCalculator.calculate(req.getMerchantId(), req.getAmountPaise());

            // 2. Build response:
            CheckResponse response = CheckResponse.newBuilder()
                .setApproved(score.isApproved())
                .setRiskScore(score.getScore())
                .setReason(score.getReason())
                .build();

            // 3. Send response and complete:
            responseObserver.onNext(response);     // send the response message
            responseObserver.onCompleted();         // signal: done sending

        } catch (IllegalArgumentException e) {
            // 4. Error: use gRPC Status codes:
            responseObserver.onError(
                Status.INVALID_ARGUMENT
                    .withDescription(e.getMessage())
                    .asRuntimeException()
            );
        }
    }
}
```

concept_explanation.grpc_client:
**gRPC client with @GrpcClient:**

```yaml
# application.yml (payment-service):
grpc:
  client:
    risk-engine:
      address: static://risk-engine.prod.svc.cluster.local:9090
      negotiation-type: plaintext  # or TLS
```

```java
@Service
public class PaymentService {
    // @GrpcClient: Spring injects the stub, manages the channel
    @GrpcClient("risk-engine")  // must match application.yml key
    private RiskServiceGrpc.RiskServiceBlockingStub riskStub; // sync call

    public PaymentResult createPayment(PaymentRequest req) {
        // gRPC call (blocking stub blocks until response):
        CheckRequest checkReq = CheckRequest.newBuilder()
            .setMerchantId(req.getMerchantId())
            .setAmountPaise(req.getAmountPaise())
            .build();

        try {
            CheckResponse risk = riskStub.checkPayment(checkReq);
            if (!risk.getApproved()) {
                return PaymentResult.rejected(risk.getReason());
            }
            return executePayment(req);
        } catch (StatusRuntimeException e) {
            if (e.getStatus().getCode() == Status.Code.UNAVAILABLE) {
                return PaymentResult.serviceUnavailable();
            }
            throw e;
        }
    }
}
```

